{{% examples %}}
## Example Usage
{{% example %}}

```typescript
import * as pulumi from "@pulumi/pulumi";
import * as buildkite from "@pulumi/buildkite";

const repo2 = pulumi.output(buildkite.getPipeline({
    slug: "repo2",
}));
```
